Basics<pre><code>git init &lt;directory&gt; 

git clone &lt;repository&gt;

git config user.name &lt;name&gt;

git add &lt;directory&gt; 

git commit -m "&lt;message&gt;"

git status

git log 

git diff
</code></pre> Workflow<pre><code>git clone &lt;repository&gt;

git status

git add &lt;directory&gt; 

git commit -m "&lt;message&gt;"

git push

git checkout -b "&lt;branch&gt;"
</code></pre>
